            <td>Warriors lead 3-1</td>
            <td>The series looks like it has no hope.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Game 5</td>
            <td>June 13, 2016</td>
            <td>Cavs 112, Warriors 97</td>
            <td>Warriors lead 3-2</td>
            <td>LeBron and Kyrie had 41 points but Warriors lead 3-2.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Game 6</td>
            <td>June 16, 2016</td>
            <td>Cavs 115, Warriors 101</td>
            <td>Series tied 3-3</td>
            <td>LeBron 41 points again, Kyrie adds 23 to force Game 7.</td>
          </tr>
